What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Bread Processing Equipment Market?



Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Bread Processing Equipment Market

The bread processing equipment market size is expected to show a value of USD 7.73 billion by 2028 growing at a compound annual rate of 7% in the forecast period 2021 to 2028. The rise in the product acceptance and usage is the factor responsible for the growth of bread processing equipment market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

Bread processing equipment refers to the devices used in moulding or makeup stages of dough to the manufacture of bread. The devices help in procedures such as mixing, fermentation, makeup, proofing, baking, cooling, slicing and packaging. These equipment are generally used in bakery, bread factory and other manufacturing industries.

The surging automation and robotics in bakery processing equipment across the world is major factor contributing for growth in market. Additionally, the factors such as increasing demand for greater variety of bread with ethnic breads and owing to their nutritional benefits, the increasing preference for healthy breads amongst health-conscious population such as fortified, clean label and organic bread across the world are estimated to contribute to growth of the bread processing equipment market. However, the refined carbohydrates in some types of bread tends to get stored as fat in the body and also elevates blood sugar levels which is projected to act as a restraint.

Moreover, the developments and innovations in bread processing equipment is estimated to further generate new opportunities for the market in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028.

